g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5745442253b3f9bb495e96db4edcba40d2996605","tid":395020,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T14:32:45.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c95cd39618f399f86fea0529163d73b1bd07ce","tid":395020,"uid":7306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T14:43:19.000Z","msg":"諾貝爾獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n光纖<br />\n全世界受惠<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ae6dabd69cebd2bf55d32395d7db66a5da11b17","tid":395020,"uid":30476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T15:55:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諾貝爾獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n光纖<br />\n全世界受惠<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我成日諗如果光纖早十五年<br />\n香港未必要回歸"},{"pid":"746fe42d1a5d67edd334d0487bc1d9db8da785af","tid":395020,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T15:56:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>諾貝爾獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n光纖<br />\n全世界受惠<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我成日諗如果光纖早十五年<br />\n香港未必要回歸</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1982年如果有互聯網同紅登<br />\n<br />\n我地獨立左<br />\n<br />\n香港民族主義遲左30年"},{"pid":"2c1a7cc86bc4edb5831744a9be1c262a2a41e9b8","tid":395020,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T16:17:27.000Z","msg":"天佑我山城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f68ce918215030e4e01fedcf2157e503d0d0b1","tid":395020,"uid":3520,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T16:21:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>依家收咗教大學生走得最前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可惜校長同當年中大高校長差十萬九千里<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實前唔前係用咩定義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n引用上邊個段<br />\n<br />\n「大學校園，本來就該是引發思潮、帶動社會前進的地方，如果我們的步伐和界線，都與外面社會的一模一樣，那又豈能起到帶動的作用呢？」"},{"pid":"5df984ab8773533e1428624c88ee5ca2dc6bab55","tid":395020,"uid":2641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T17:21:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>依家收咗教大學生走得最前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可惜校長同當年中大高校長差十萬九千里<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實前唔前係用咩定義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n引用上邊個段<br />\n<br />\n「大學校園，本來就該是引發思潮、帶動社會前進的地方，如果我們的步伐和界線，都與外面社會的一模一樣，那又豈能起到帶動的作用呢？」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n社會上基本上除左大學就唔會有機構有咁既作用"},{"pid":"9d7ddee3623b53bb9edc6cb95e3072438de54975","tid":395020,"uid":14423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T17:32:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>諾貝爾獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n光纖<br />\n全世界受惠<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我成日諗如果光纖早十五年<br />\n香港未必要回歸</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1982年如果有互聯網同紅登<br />\n<br />\n我地獨立左<br />\n<br />\n香港民族主義遲左30年</blockquote><br />\n2008 京奧果陣，高登咪又係奶共<br />\n根本係要俾香港人同中國有多啲接觸先會知中國有幾仆街，關撚互聯網事<br />\n但高錕真係值得尊敬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f65173383163c01f96f228edede6da656d3c7f","tid":395020,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T17:33:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我記得80年代初「香港前途談判」，中大同學冒著天下之大不韙，提出香港應該脫離港英殖民管治，民主回歸祖國。當時在這個醉生夢死的殖民社會，這是何等的離經叛道，與所謂的「主流社會標準」，差距又豈能以道里計，公眾也是絕不接受，甚至更罵同學為「共諜」、「死左仔」。更有聲音說這些中大同學畢業後公司將永不錄用，甚至催促中大應予以警誡。<span style=\"color: red;\">但20年後，事實證明，究竟又是誰對誰錯呢？</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n梗係你班死左仔錯啦！</blockquote><br />\n根本就係共諜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n30年後，事實證明，究竟又是誰對誰錯呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1be285af519ea3d6aa82ea7f3595b7fe33edcbc","tid":395020,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T17:35:48.000Z","msg":"吹乜鳩，咪又係投共，你唔好同我講佢處理得比較好就可以掩蓋投共嘅事實呀"},{"pid":"12bede69d1c0f507f1f9fd23f27350f7a75566de","tid":395020,"uid":141131,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T17:42:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>依家收咗教大學生走得最前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可惜校長同當年中大高校長差十萬九千里<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實前唔前係用咩定義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n引用上邊個段<br />\n<br />\n「大學校園，本來就該是引發思潮、帶動社會前進的地方，如果我們的步伐和界線，都與外面社會的一模一樣，那又豈能起到帶動的作用呢？」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n社會上基本上除左大學就唔會有機構有咁既作用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而然，現今的大學，不過是一商店，為企業開發未來的奴動力，不再是甚麼孕育思想的學府了"},{"pid":"72e76ec88a907ed817ff99678383db9e1335166c","tid":395020,"uid":2641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T17:44:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>依家收咗教大學生走得最前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可惜校長同當年中大高校長差十萬九千里<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實前唔前係用咩定義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n引用上邊個段<br />\n<br />\n「大學校園，本來就該是引發思潮、帶動社會前進的地方，如果我們的步伐和界線，都與外面社會的一模一樣，那又豈能起到帶動的作用呢？」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n社會上基本上除左大學就唔會有機構有咁既作用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而然，現今的大學，不過是一商店，為企業開